        </p>
        <h3>5.4. Taxes</h3>
        <p>
            Prices displayed are exclusive of applicable sales tax, VAT, GST, or similar taxes,
            which we may add and collect where required by law.
        </p>
        <h3>5.5. Cancellation and refunds</h3>
        <p>
            You may cancel at any time from <code>/account/billing</code>. Cancellation takes effect
            at the end of the current billing period; you retain access through that period.
            <strong>Fees already paid are non-refundable</strong> except where required by law or
            where service was materially defective due to our fault. To request a refund for a
            service defect, contact <strong>@LegalSettingsService.Or(_settings?.ContactEmail, "CONTACT EMAIL")</strong> within <strong>14 days</strong>
            of the charge.
        </p>
        <h3>5.6. Plan downgrades and overages</h3>
        <p>
            If you downgrade to a plan with a lower animal or team-member limit and your current
            usage exceeds that limit, you must reduce usage to comply within <strong>14 days</strong>.
            We may restrict creation of new records on the downgraded plan until you comply.
        </p>
        <h3>5.7. Account deletion and grace period</h3>
        <p>
            You may delete your account from <code>/account/settings</code>. Your account and all
            Farms where you are the sole Owner will be <strong>soft-deleted</strong> immediately
            (hidden, billing canceled) and <strong>permanently deleted after 30 days</strong>. During
            the grace period you may contact us to restore the account. After hard deletion,
            recovery is not possible.
        </p>

