            <li>Storing backups for disaster recovery.</li>
            <li>Aggregating de-identified usage statistics for product analytics.</li>
            <li>Displaying Customer Content publicly <strong>only</strong> when you explicitly opt
                in (e.g., enabling your public Farm page or marking individual goats as listed for
                sale).</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>7.3. Public Farm pages</h3>
        <p>
            If you enable a public Farm page, the goats you mark "for sale" will be viewable at
            <code>https://goatlab.app/pub/{your-slug}/{goat-id}</code> by anyone with the link,
