            breed, registration, asking price, contact email, pedigree). You are responsible for
            ensuring you have the right to publish this information and that it is accurate. Do not
            include personal data of third parties.
        </p>
        <h3>7.4. Backups</h3>
        <p>
            We perform periodic backups of the database for disaster recovery. We do not guarantee
            any specific backup retention or recovery-time objective for your individual data; you
            are responsible for maintaining your own copies of mission-critical records via the
            <strong>Export my data</strong> function in <code>/account/settings</code>.
        </p>
        <h3>7.5. Data export</h3>
        <p>
            At any time, you may export a copy of your data in machine-readable (JSON/CSV) format
            from <code>/account/settings</code>. We will retain the ability to respond to export
            requests for at least the duration of your active subscription plus the 30-day deletion
